        Saves an event to the queue.
        Parameters:
        link - URL of the event postback
        eventItems - (Optional) MATEventItem JSON information to post to server
        action - the action for the event (conversion/install/open)
        revenue - value associated with the event
        currency - currency code for the revenue
        refId - the advertiser ref ID associated with the event
        iapData - the receipt data from Google Play
        iapSignature - the receipt signature from Google Play
        shouldBuildData - whether link needs encrypted data to be appended or not
        runDate - datetime for request to be made
